nodes.text: Gnasps were a species of dangerous, large, wasp-like insects native to the moon Alaris Prime, and also found in the forests of Kashyyyk, the planet Alaris orbited. They lived in swarms and were known for stinging.
The species gave its name to the Raddaugh Gnasp fluttercraft, a model of ornithopter manufactured by Appazanna Engineering Works.
